flowchart TB
    A[Square2CNF predicate\nphi = (l1 OR l2) AND (l3 OR l4)] --> B{Branch}
    B -->|True branch| C[Encode clauses:\n[l1 OR l2]\n[l3 OR l4]]
    C --> D[2-CNF]
    D --> E[ExactSATSolver.two_sat]

    B -->|False branch| F[Encode NOT(phi) with auxiliary switch s]
    F --> F1[(not s OR not l1)]
    F --> F2[(not s OR not l2)]
    F --> F3[(s OR not l3)]
    F --> F4[(s OR not l4)]
    F1 --> G[2-CNF]
    F2 --> G
    F3 --> G
    F4 --> G
    G --> H[ExactSATSolver.two_sat]

    E --> I[Theorem-certified only when:\ntheorem_strict=True\nbackend=two_sat\npath_certificate=2cnf]
    H --> I
